songs.title: All Alone*
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Hahaha... Nick, you're stupid
Yeehaw

[Chorus]
All alone (All alone)
Fighting (Fighting)
On my own (On my own)
Fighting (Fighting)
All alone (All alone)
Fighting-ing (Fighting)
On my own (On my own)
Fighting (Fighting)

[Verse 1]
Drawn out my sleep, demons haunting
Me and my memories (My memories)
Did this happen? (Did this happen?)
Was that a dream?
I, I, I can't-
